      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be verified under a documented SQA plan with version control and regression testing.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent v19.2 used under an FDA-recognized SQA framework. Version-controlled simulation files, regression test suite, and documented build verification confirm SQA level 2 compliance."
    },
    {
