      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must pass method of manufactured solutions (MMS) or equivalent benchmark for the governing equations applied.",
      "rationale": "Fluent v19.2 has been verified against ASME V&V 20 benchmark cases for incompressible turbulent flow. MMS results for the k-omega SST turbulence model confirm second-order spatial accuracy."
